issue.title: MDCT-116: Run Cypress on Deploy
issue.body:
# Description

Adding `Cypress` to GitHub actions workflow.

## How to test

See that it ran on this branch!

## Dependencies

N/A

# Get it done

Cypress is running.

## Code authors checklist

- [ ] I have performed a self-review of my code
- [ ] I have added thorough tests. [Testing Doc](https://qmacbis.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/CM/pages/2914025525/Test+Suite+and+Testing+Research)
- [ ] Necessary analytics were added, or no new analytics were required
- [ ] I have made corresponding changes to the documentation
- [ ] I have assigned the PR to myself

## Reviewers Checklist (Two different people)

- [ ] I have done the deep review and verified the items in the above checklist are g2g
- [ ] I have done the lgtm review

## Assignee

- [ ] I have closed the PR after the review and necessary changes (squashing preferred)
